\id PHP - Matupi Chin Standard Bible With Strong's Number
\h PHILIPI
\toc1 PHILIPI
\toc2 Philipi
\toc3 Phil
\mt1 PHILIPI
\mt4 (Letter to the Philippians)
\is2 Philipi Capat Kawng
\im Paul loh hekah ca he thongim ah a tael ( 1.7) tih Philipi hlangboel taengah a pat. Philipi Khrihca rhoek nen khaw thangthuinah dongah pat mueh la pha uh thae (1.5; 4.10-19). Thongim lamloh a loeih atah olthangthen thui ham a ngaiuep (3.17-19). Tedae Paul loh amah kah a dueknah ham kawng khaw a ming. (1.21; 2.17; 3.10).
\ip Philipi khopuei he tah Greek ram tlangpuei ah om tih, Greek rhoek long tah Makedonia a ti uh. Europe ram khuiah tah Paul loh a phanah cuek lah om tih olthangthen a thui nah, hlangboel a tongnah la om (Clt 16). Jesuh loh patang a khang bangla Paul amah khaw patang a khang, hlang boel loh a patang a khang khaw thapaek hloepnah a thui. Te long te Khrih tangnah rhangneh yoethennah a thoeng sak kawng a thui. (1.28-30).
\ip Philipi hlangboel khuiah tuituknah bet aka om tah daemnah aka om thai pawh olkhueng rhuem bangla khosak a ngoe aka ti a om dongah. Olkhueng rhuem la aka cet rhoek tah Paul long tah a tloh la a voek tih ui a ti nah (3.2-11). Paul he thongim ah om dae Khrih a khueh dongah omngaihnah soep a khueh tih Khrihca hlang boel rhoek khaw khueh uh van a ti nah. Hekah capat he tah \sc a.d\sc* 61-62 tluk kah Ephesa thongim ah a om vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Kuttuk neh Thangthuinah (1.1-11)
\io1 Khosaknah neh hingnah kawng (1.12-30)
\io1 Khrih kah kodo thindo (2.1-18)
\io1 Paul paya kah olthang kali (2.19-30)
\io1 Pathen kah doenah (3.1—4.9)
\io1 Philipi taengah omngaihcil (4.10-20)
\io1 Hnukkhueng kah olnoi (4.21-23)
\c 1
\s1 Uemnah Ol
\p 
